articles.author: Ellen Rittiner
articles.title: American medics are stuck in Gaza. Hear one doctor’s message to the US government - CNN
articles.description: CNN’s Jeremy Diamond speaks to American doctors stuck in Gaza after the Rafah crossing closed since the Israeli military seized it.
articles.content: CNN's Jeremy Diamond speaks to American medical workers stuck in Gaza after an Israeli military offensive in Rafah shuttered the critical border crossing into Egypt.
